'''拉斐特学院'''（{{lang-en|Lafayette College}}）为一所坐落在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]][[伊斯顿_(宾夕法尼亚州)|伊斯顿]]的[[私立大學|私立]][[美国文理学院|文理学院]]，在纽约市有一个小型卫星校区。1826年詹姆斯·麦迪逊·波特和伊斯顿的其他市民一起创建拉斐特学院，学院第一次授课是在1832年<ref name= "historyoflaf">{{cite web | url = http://www.lafayette.edu/about/history/ | title = History of Lafayette College | publisher = Lafayette College | accessdate=2020-09-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100904114434/http://www.lafayette.edu/about/history/ | archive-date = 2010-09-04 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。创始人投票决定以[[拉斐德侯爵|拉斐德侯爵]]的名字来命名该所学院。

拉斐特学院既被认为是一个[[隐藏的常春藤盟校|隐藏的常春藤盟校]]<ref>{{Cite book|title = Greenes' Guides to Educational Planning: The Hidden Ivies: Thirty Colleges of Excellence|last = Greene|first = Howard|publisher = HarperCollins|year = 2000|isbn = 0-06-095362-4|location = New York|pages = |last2 = Greene|first2 = Matthew W.}}</ref>，又是[[美国东北部|东北部]]的一所[[小常春藤盟校|小常春藤盟校]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-12-22/little-good-news-for-the-little-ivies|title=The Little Ivies' Endowments Took a Big Hit This Year|date=2016-12-22|work=Bloomberg.com|accessdate=2020-09-26|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023124014/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-12-22/little-good-news-for-the-little-ivies|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

